STATE

Ralph F. FREDRICK. No. 363P03-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 27, 2007. Anne M. Middleton, Assistant Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of NC.

*392The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd day of April 2007 by Defendant for Petition for Rehearing of N.C. Court of Appeals Order:
